---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect personal data."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40vh">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1450101499163-c8848c66ca85?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>How ARM Management collects, uses, and protects your personal data.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:#9CA3AF;margin-bottom:40px">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:24px">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">ARM Management is an international business advisory headquartered in the United Arab Emirates with advisory operations across the European Union, GCC, Asia Pacific, and Latin America. References to "ARM Management", "we", "us", or "our" in this policy refer to the ARM Management group of entities.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px">For data protection enquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@arm-management.com" style="color:#B8960C">info@arm-management.com</a></p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">We collect personal data that you voluntarily provide to us, including:</p>
      <ul class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px;padding-left:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px">
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Name, email address, and company details submitted via our contact form</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Information you share in correspondence with our advisors</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Technical data such as IP address and browser type collected automatically when you visit our website</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Analytics data collected via Google Analytics (anonymised)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">We use the personal data we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="reveal" style="margin-top:16px;padding-left:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px">
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Respond to enquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Deliver advisory services to clients under a formal service agreement</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Improve our website and understand how visitors use it</li>
        <li style="font-size:16px;color:#4B5563;line-height:1.8">Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">4. Data Retention</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">We retain personal data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal, regulatory, accounting, or reporting requirements. Enquiry data from non-clients is retained for 12 months. Client data is retained for the duration of the engagement and for seven years thereafter in accordance with standard legal and regulatory requirements.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Depending on your jurisdiction of residence, you may have rights including: the right to access personal data we hold about you; the right to correct inaccurate data; the right to request deletion; and the right to object to processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@arm-management.com" style="color:#B8960C">info@arm-management.com</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">6. Cookies</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Our website uses Google Analytics to understand site usage. Google Analytics places cookies on your device to collect anonymised data. You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" style="color:#B8960C" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>. We do not use advertising, tracking, or third-party marketing cookies.</p>

      <h2 class="reveal" style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-top:56px;margin-bottom:24px">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The most current version will always be available at arm-management.com/privacy-policy. Continued use of our website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:56px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6" class="reveal">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
